{"content":"---\ntitle: \"Derived classes cannot raise base class events\"\nms.date: 07/20/2015\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"vbc30029\"\n  - \"bc30029\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"BC30029\"\nms.assetid: 63afa1c6-2f93-4512-a2f0-372455979771\n---\n# Derived classes cannot raise base class events\nAn event can be raised only from the declaration space in which it is declared. Therefore, a class cannot raise events from any other class, even one from which it is derived.  \n  \n **Error ID:** BC30029  \n  \n## To correct this error  \n  \n-   Move the `Event` statement or the `RaiseEvent` statement so they are in the same class.  \n  \n## See also\n\n- [Event Statement](../../../visual-basic/language-reference/statements/event-statement.md)\n- [RaiseEvent Statement](../../../visual-basic/language-reference/statements/raiseevent-statement.md)\n","nodes":[{"pos":[4,207],"embed":true,"restype":"x-metadata","content":"title: \"Derived classes cannot raise base class events\"\nms.date: 07/20/2015\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"vbc30029\"\n  - \"bc30029\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"BC30029\"\nms.assetid: 63afa1c6-2f93-4512-a2f0-372455979771","nodes":[{"content":"Derived classes cannot raise base class events","nodes":[{"pos":[0,46],"content":"Derived classes cannot raise base class events","nodes":[{"content":"Derived classes cannot raise base class events","pos":[0,46]}]}],"path":["title"],"nosxs":false}],"yml":true},{"pos":[214,260],"content":"Derived classes cannot raise base class events","linkify":"Derived classes cannot raise base class events","nodes":[{"content":"Derived classes cannot raise base class events","pos":[0,46]}]},{"content":"An event can be raised only from the declaration space in which it is declared.","pos":[261,340]},{"content":"Therefore, a class cannot raise events from any other class, even one from which it is derived.","pos":[341,436]},{"pos":[443,464],"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Error ID:<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> BC30029","source":"**Error ID:** BC300